  "detailed_description": "<strong>Hello fellow mechanic,</strong><br><br>You've been called to fix an elevator in the gorgeous <i>Castela d'Alpine Manor</i>.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.poster.avif?t=1730209882\" width=616 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.webm?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/32d481df7fa5b3d9e1692283968f9565.mp4?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Your job: <strong><i>Reach the 10th floor to restore the elevator and</i> <u>escape safely.</u></strong></h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Stay vigilant<br></li><li>Inspect every corner for anything out of the ordinary<br></li><li>Check every door<br></li><li>Be brave</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.poster.avif?t=1730209882\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.webm?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/eef7407617cce3efc16d426e2693ec2a.mp4?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Important:</strong> Every detail counts! Anomalies may show as subtle changes in sounds, objects, images, and lights.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.poster.avif?t=1730209882\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.webm?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/03e85942a6b11ed38efe2a44c51e1b79.mp4?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Encounter an anomaly? Hasten back to the emergency stairs.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.poster.avif?t=1730209882\" width=616 height=196 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.webm?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/fd96f9e6062053d7e2081cefaea67fbf.mp4?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Description</h2>Step into the shoes of a mechanic summoned to fix an elevator in a mysterious 1930s hotel. As you delve deeper into the building's haunted hallways, you'll face eerie anomalies and uncover the dark secrets lurking within. <br><br>Could you finish your job and escape safely?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>1930s Hotel Theme<br></li><li>Playtime: 20-50 minutes<br></li><li>3 Endings (Neutral, Bad, Secret)<br></li><li>25 Achievements</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls</h2> <ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>WASD: Move <br></li><li>Left Click: Interact <br></li><li>Right Click: Zoom <br></li><li>Shift: Run <br></li><li>ESC: Options</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/796716508fde8058056614ddc689a275.avif?t=1730209882\" width=428 height=152 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/dee86c78a08824b0f20e663910bf50af.poster.avif?t=1730209882\" width=188 height=154 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2991500/extras/dee86c78a08824b0f20e663910bf50af.webm?t=1730209882\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
